{"tid":2516003,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"公司出糧出多咗個零","createTime":"2021-05-04T10:59:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T11:23:01.000Z","uid":376170,"like":102,"dislike":245,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"c770afc07aebced32de7f9cdea8cf5eee24ed1b1","tid":2516003,"uid":376170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T10:59:54.000Z","msg":"番緊嗰份工係用支票出糧<br />\n每個月定時定候入腦細房攞支票<br />\n糧就係固定嘅，唔洗跑數開單<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啱啱趁lunch有時間剩就諗住去入票<br />\n點知一拎出嚟見到張cheque多咗個0<br />\n以為攞錯咗人哋嗰張<br />\n睇清楚個信封係寫我個名<br />\n第一感覺一定係好撚爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無啦啦多咗成九個月人工喎<br />\n<br />\n但係諗諗吓<br />\n邊有咁大隻蛤乸隨街跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cross.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n會唔會係佢想試吓我對公司忠誠度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講咗話唔定會升職<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我究竟應唔應該同個細細講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔講"},{"pid":"c5cf0725265b1cfd159998c687a226cd5267fcbf","tid":2516003,"uid":353080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T11:00:56.000Z","msg":"我係1"},{"pid":"9626012ace8430ef7120c16a62d91c902885df2c","tid":2516003,"uid":366207,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T11:01:03.000Z","msg":"咪玩啦Ching 呢個問題嚟嘅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69f22270689b9f734b74f161a2fdb08715732b3a","tid":2516003,"uid":20619,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T11:01:20.000Z","msg":"白鳩痴"},{"pid":"1d082b3bdf2af674505659a5bdabb54d8bd259eb","tid":2516003,"uid":52942,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T11:02:06.000Z","msg":"你升幾多之職先補得到個0<img src=\"/assets/faces