或借出該財產，亦可相當於不顧另一人的權利而將該財產視為自己的財產處置。<br />\n(2)在以不損害第(1)款的概括性為原則下，凡任何人管有或控制(不論是否合法地管有或控制)屬於另一人的財產，而為他自己的目的及未得該另一人授權，在未必能履行將該財產歸還的條件下放棄該財產，即相當於不顧該另一人的權利而將財產視為自己的財產處置。<br />\n[比照 1968 c. 60 s. 6 U.K.]</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap210!zh-Hant-HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap210%21zh-Hant-HK&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordK98yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=5612d92f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap210!zh-Hant-HK</a><br />\n<br />\n利申: 9 up，真係擔心勸你揾下免費法律諮詢"},{"pid":"25e2768c07dca9f72a08f9a6a98dfdbb33a2fa1b","tid":2516003,"uid":70846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T11:07:33.000Z","msg":"不過樓主可以search 吓<br />\n外國有人可以話出錯糧照拎<br />\n<br />\n不過又 0可以寫多一個 個全寫唔會錯㗎喎<br />\n我係咪真心咗"},{"pid":"552a08510fd37d8a42560ea0f443a4c3a7e418a1","tid":2516003,"uid":27251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T11:07:38.000Z","msg":"唔好搏啦"},{"pid":"ca4436a4b93de3cd498c9e2eeca16a242f673674","tid":2516003,"uid":99642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"587c94b9e72d4190d5cc6cbdaaa72777b48b2d38","tid":2516003,"uid":376170,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9626012ace8430ef7120c16a62d91c902885df2c","tid":2516003,"uid":366207,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T11:01:03.000Z","msg":"咪玩啦Ching 呢個問題嚟嘅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T11:02:56.000Z","msg":"我真係驚佢陰鳩我"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T11:08:14.000Z","msg":"陰乜尻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n扮唔知<br />\nKeep住筆錢唔用一年"},{"pid":"ede0f6e25680fbefd4cdb63ab28ddd8710e2ec22","tid":2516003,"uid":376170,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T11:08:45.000Z","msg":"點解負皮會多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"257bb4352226f7ef7fd27b9333a778fd1e725